         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Thornbury. Suva. Fiji ¶ 13th January 1883 ¶ My dear Sir, ¶  ¶ I have been quite unable to answer your note of the 29 Nov. last ¶ Letter not found. ¶  ¶ in consequence of our Legislative Council having...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.01.13</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Thurston</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M129, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS found with specimens of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Cycas seemannii</seg>.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>MS annotation by M: 'Answ 23/1/83'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Thornbury. Suva. Fiji</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">13th January 1883</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have been quite unable to answer your note of the 29 Nov. last<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in consequence of our Legislative Council having been in session and my time wholly given to official duties.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This note is just to forward you some scales of the cone of a Male Cycas which I have at last found.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="frame"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The cone is from two to two<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp; a half feet long and 4.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or 4½<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>inches in diameter in its greatest breadth —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>General shape, long, and pointed. The end when quite ripe bending over.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This sentence is accompanied by a sketch by Thurston showing the shape of the cone.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>83-01-13_image01.jpg</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The specimens<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>were taken in the vicinity of a number of female trees the whole of which, without exception, were of the round seed variety, not the long, oval, one. The cone emits a strong perfume &amp; reminds me of the smell of salted codfish when rather strong.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall await with interest your examination of these scales, but will write you more at length via New Zealand</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Have you had time amid your pressing duties to [decide] of the coco-nut of a new variety I sent you some time since, with straight unbranched spadix?<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>specimen not identified.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have found a perfectly new Fan Palm, hitherto unseen &amp; unnoticed by any one. Specimens shall be sent to you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Faithfully yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John B. Thurston.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Cycas</p>
         </div>
